<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="5Feb1934"><font color="red">5 February 1934</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): Mr Morely &hellip; asks whether the specimen page for Work in Progress which he sent is satisfactory to Mr Joyce &hellip; If Mr Joyce does approve, then Fabers can get ahead with the setting up of the part of the text in hand. They are ready to begin any time Mr Joyce gives the approval of the page. </div>
